column5: Is it working Mel? If it makes you feel any better, I have not done much damage to your walleye population, yet.
Cabin Fever starting to break up here in Kansas. Actually been fishing small rivers and catching a few eyes. Sure feels good. Mike Kansas
Cabin fever in Iowa. 64 deays till Lake of the Woods!!!!!!!!!!
But what will you use the second day? Bill
Bill, I'll have to use the crankbaits I just finished painting!!!!!
Cabin fever in Canada, had to go outside to relieve the stress. http://i1178.photobucket.com/albums/...psbdcd4491.jpg

Skywagon I love the Canadian way for stress relief! Wish we had Lakers in our Iowa farm ponds. Ice is almost gone on the mighty Mississippi where I live. Can finally do some softwater fishing for Eyes.
IA, dont give Skywagon any encouragement, He comes in here with photos for one reason and one reason only. TO PISS THE REST OF US OFF!!!!!!!LOL Steve
